Families
========
O: kanjiVariant '-04' is supported.
P: We have '-04' maps, but fonts lack some glyphs
X: We don't have '-04' maps.

O noEmbed
    (no font needed for dvipdfmx)

X ms
    msmincho.ttc
    msgothic.ttc
X ipa
    ipam.ttf
    ipag.ttf
X ipaex
    ipaexm.ttf
    ipaexg.ttf

O? hiragino-pro
    HiraMinPro-W2.otf
    HiraMinPro-W3.otf
    HiraMinPro-W6.otf
    HiraKakuPro-W3.otf
    HiraKakuPro-W6.otf
    HiraKakuStd-W8.otf
    HiraMaruPro-W4.otf

O hiragino-pron
    same with ProN/StdN instead of Pro/Std

P kozuka-pro
    KozMinPro-Light.otf
    KozMinPro-Regular.otf
    KozMinPro-Bold.otf
    KozGoPro-Light.otf
    KozGoPro-Regular.otf
    KozGoPro-Bold.otf
    KozGoPro-Heavy.otf

O kozuka-pr6n
    same with Pr6N instead of Pro

P morisawa-pro
    A-OTF-FutoGoB101Pro-Bold.otf
    A-OTF-FutoMinA101Pro-Bold.otf
    A-OTF-GothicBBBPro-Medium.otf
    A-OTF-Jun101Pro-Light.otf
    A-OTF-MidashiGoPro-MB31.otf
    A-OTF-RyuminPro-Light.otf

O morisawa-pr6n
    same with Pr6N instead of Pro
